data.description: This sweet 2-bedroom 2 bath Low Country Cottage on Dataw Island is a renovator's dream! An abundance of natural light, cathedral ceilings in the Great room and an open floor plan. Board and batten exterior, a separate two car garage and a great location on Dataw Island.  This home is a fabulous opportunity for those who love fixer uppers. Rental properties are in high demand on Dataw Island and this home could be the perfect income generating property.  Come check out this sweet one-story bungalow and see for yourself! As an owner on Dataw Island, you will have access to lifestyle amenities including a resort style pool, two 18-hole championship golf courses, 8 tennis courts, a full-service marina, 4 pickleball courts, bocce, an art center and much more. Located just six miles from the beautiful historic downtown of Beaufort and the pristine beaches of Hunting Island State Park. Membership in Dataw Island is required.
